_______________________________________________________________________________
"Displace"   
        This power allows the psionicist to create an image of himself
        in people's minds while he himself is actually a short distance
        away!  The effect of the power is to create a 'dummy' of the
        psionicist that does not attack but draws the attacks of any
        opponents, who believe it to be the original psionicist.  This
        is a very powerful ability.  After a length of time dependent on
        guild level, the opponents will realize their mistake and begin
        attacking the real psionicist again. 
 
SP Cost:  60		Guild Level:  10	Potential Points:  5
 
Command:  displace
